dialogue: A possibility I foresaw, yet one I hoped wouldn't come to pass.
Our axe has turned wayward at promise of strength.
One without a way is easily drawn to the promise of wealth.
Please! This has to be some kind of misunderstanding!
I don't know what your plan is, but I've got your back!
You can't be serious, {pl}! You wish to side with Dragonlord!?
A possibility I foresaw, yet one I hoped wouldn't come to pass.
Our axe has turned wayward at promise of strength.
One without a way is easily drawn to the promise of wealth.
Please! This has to be some kind of misunderstanding!
I can't! {pl}... if this is the path you wish to take then I can't stay by your side.
<<[i]My heart lies with the Yuan Dao![/i]>>
